Text:
By Thor's sweaty jock strap! Bestek what are you trying to do to us? this is down right scary, I think I may be scared for the remainder of my life. You have a reputation for posting awesome pictures of gorgeous women, and now this! have you sustained a head injury? did you get a bad batch of Brown acid from Woodstock? 
(I think I just threw up a bit in my mouth.)
Please excuse me while I go wash my eyeballs with bleach.
